<h2 id="live-it-out">Live It Out</h2>
<p class="lead">End each week with a challenge to take action. Here are some ideas for tools that could help you stay on track.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Start a Bible habit with the YouVersion 21-Day New Year Challenge. You could win an iPad and other prizes! Info at <a href="http://blog.youversion.com">http://blog.youversion.com</a></li>
  <li>Start a fast with your group and follow this 21-Day Fast reading plan. <a href="https://www.bible.com/reading-plans/35-21-day-fast">https://www.bible.com/reading-plans/35-21-day-fast</a></li>
  <li>Try attending a weekend Life.Church experience every week in January. Make plans to attend together as a group for accountability (and fun)!</li>
</ul>
